    dc:creator "Hernandez, Osvaldo; Gomez-Gutierrez, Jaime; Galvan-Tirado, Carolina; Sanchez, Carlos" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of the sea fan genus Muricea (Cnidaria, Octocorallia, Plexauridae) from the northwest region of Mexico" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figurel>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure8>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure4> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figurel>
    dc:description "Figure l. Locations of sample collections of the three new species of the genus Muricea discovered along the Pacific coast of Baja California Sur and the Gulf of California, Mexico A scuba diving and monitoring census sites B Muricea ambarae sp. nov. collection sites C Muricea cacao sp. nov. collection sites D Muricea molinai sp. nov. collection sites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/880609" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Muricea ambarae sp. nov. A holotype USNM 1606629 B holotype detail of branches C axial and coenenchymal sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/880610" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Muricea ambarae sp. nov. SEM A, B calycular and coenenchymal sclerites C axial sclerites D anthocodial sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/880611" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Sea fan colonies photographed in situ A, B Muricea ambarae sp. nov. C, D Muricea cacao sp. nov. E-G Muricea molinai sp. nov. Photographs by Carlos Sanchez." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/880616" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1169.89651.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Muricea cacao sp. nov. A holotype USNM 1606633 B anthocodial and coenenchymal sclerites C holotype detail of branches." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/880612" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

